show.description: Vera, the wealthy daughter of the Smith Group, loses her memory in a mishap and is taken in by a poor family. Years later, she reenters the Smith Group workforce as Samantha, a financially struggling woman. Samantha faces constant hardships from her brother Bert and biological mother due to her humble background. Fate plays a hand as she falls in love with her brother Joseph. However, as Samantha's true identity slowly emerges, the future of this taboo love becomes uncertain...
